N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 257.11 - Registration

State Regulations

The registration year for pet food and specialty pet food
as required by section 129(2) of the law shall be the calendar year. Applications for such registration shall be made, and all annual fees required
by the law shall be paid on or before the first day of December for the
following calendar year. Notes
